headline: Nasdaq Correction: Is This High-Yield Dividend Stock the Right Place to Run for Cover?
summary: Right now, investors are clearly selling assets, but they are also looking for a new home for the cash that's raised.  One beneficiary has been high-yielding Kraft Heinz (NASDAQ: KHC).  When stock markets fall beyond key yardsticks, investors start to worry.

summary: CHICAGO, March 10, 2025--Last October, a viral social media video mixing diet cola with pickle juice racked up more than 12 million views, sparking thousands of comments.
